title: Choose Problem
on-departure: display_fltr = 1

Facilyn: Let’s place your holistic context to the left, so you can keep it in view.

She slides a new sheet of paper on the table.

Facilyn: To use this holistic context, we’ll run decisions through seven testing questions. They filter out actions that look good today, but take you off course tomorrow.

Facilyn: What kind of problem do you want to work through as an example?

- #choose_prblm

@prblm_explanation
title: Are the filter questions different
subtitle: from an ordinary pros-and-cons list?
max-visits: 1
order: 21
tags: choose_prblm

Me: Are the filter questions different from an ordinary pros-and-cons list?

Facilyn: The checks are not just a list of advantages and disadvantages. They are a set of filters designed to reveal whether an action is socially, financially, and environmentally sound in both the short and long term, relative to your Holistic Context.

- #choose_prblm

