@prblm_environmental
title: An environmental or land management decision
on-arrival: prblm_type = "An environmental or land management decision"; info_last = "Dust storms" if info_dust_storms = 0; info_dust_storms = 1
go-to: prblm_chosen
tags: choose_prblm

Me: [+ prblm_type +]

Facilyn: Wonderful. This touches on land use, conservation, sustainability practices, or environmental impact.

@prblm_agricultural
