@prblm_chosen
title: Example decision
go-to: 27_fq_cause_effect

Facilyn: To choose your solution, you consider experience, experts' or friends' advice, and laws as always.  

Facilyn: And when you come up with your preferred solution, before you take any action, you will run your decision through the seven context checks to see the likely effect on your whole. 
